{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Nv8E5ZGHTD4mUmWE7W1GZv","type":"tool_result","content":"    84→{\"id\":\"cloche-lmz\",\"title\":\"Track host workflow runs in RunStore and expose via CLI/web\",\"description\":\"Host workflow runs (e.g. main-eager-moss) are executed by the new host executor but are not persisted to the RunStore. This means they don't appear in `cloche list`, `cloche logs`, `cloche status`, or the web portal.\\n\\nHost workflow runs should be tracked alongside container runs:\\n- Persist host runs in RunStore with their state, steps, and outputs\\n- Make them visible in `cloche list` and `cloche status`\\n- Expose logs via `cloche logs`\\n- Show them in the web portal run list and detail views\\n- Distinguish them from container runs (e.g. workflow type or a host flag)\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T14:22:11.718664925-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-09T14:22:11.718664925-07:00\",\"labels\":[\"cli\",\"host-workflow\",\"web-portal\"]}\n    85→{\"id\":\"cloche-lu9\",\"title\":\"Add run title/summary to CLI status and web portal\",\"description\":\"Provide a one-line summary of the work being done in a container run. Two sources:\\n\\n1. Passed explicitly via `cloche run --title \\\"title goes here\\\"` (e.g. from a ticket title or other short description).\\n2. If not provided, cloche-agent generates a one-line summary of the prompt's request (via LLM or simple extraction) and reports it back.\\n\\nThe title should be:\\n- Stored with the run in the daemon/store\\n- Displayed in `cloche status` CLI output\\n- Shown in the web portal's run-details header section\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T14:05:41.75253649-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-09T14:05:41.75253649-07:00\",\"labels\":[\"cli\",\"web-portal\"]}"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83efa890-2574-44c5-a1f7-226ad3f671c0","uuid":"b614ef2c-dc6e-41e5-9924-111904aa04cb","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/.beads/issues.jsonl","content":"{\"id\":\"cloche-lmz\",\"title\":\"Track host workflow runs in RunStore and expose via CLI/web\",\"description\":\"Host workflow runs (e.g. main-eager-moss) are executed by the new host executor but are not persisted to the RunStore. This means they don't appear in `cloche list`, `cloche logs`, `cloche status`, or the web portal.\\n\\nHost workflow runs should be tracked alongside container runs:\\n- Persist host runs in RunStore with their state, steps, and outputs\\n- Make them visible in `cloche list` and `cloche status`\\n- Expose logs via `cloche logs`\\n- Show them in the web portal run list and detail views\\n- Distinguish them from container runs (e.g. workflow type or a host flag)\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T14:22:11.718664925-07:00\",\"created_by\":\"lucas\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-09T14:22:11.718664925-07:00\",\"labels\":[\"cli\",\"host-workflow\",\"web-portal\"]}\n{\"id\":\"cloche-lu9\",\"title\":\"Add run title/summary to CLI status and web portal\",\"description\":\"Provide a one-line summary of the work being done in a container run. Two sources:\\n\\n1. Passed explicitly via `cloche run --title \\\"title goes here\\\"` (e.g. from a ticket title or other short description).\\n2. If not provided, cloche-agent generates a one-line summary of the prompt's request (via LLM or simple extraction) and reports it back.\\n\\nThe title should be:\\n- Stored with the run in the daemon/store\\n- Displayed in `cloche status` CLI output\\n- Shown in the web portal's run-details header section\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lucas@perfectlunacy.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-